item.description:
As you probably already know, campaign HQ in Concord now has a fully functional bank of 10+ phones for doing call-in. We're heading up for our weekly "Let's give HQ a hand with call-in" evening. Third week running now. It's easy to do and It's a lot of fun when lots of folks are doing it at once. HQ really appreciates the help with call-in. Come on up! We'll run the phones from 6:30 to 8:30pm.

If you need a ride, contact myself (Jay) or Richard Laplante by email and we'll arrange some carpooling.
item.name: HQ Phone Banking
